#. <section class="sutta" id="an7.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.4:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Dhanavagga"
msgstr "1. Wealth"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 4. Vitthatabalasutta → vitthatasattabalasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an7.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Vitthatabalasutta"
msgstr "4. Powers in Detail"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an7.4:1.1"
msgid "“Sattimāni, bhikkhave, balāni."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these seven powers."

msgctxt "an7.4:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni satta?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "an7.4:1.3"
msgid ""
"Saddhābalaṃ, vīriyabalaṃ, hirībalaṃ, ottappabalaṃ, satibalaṃ, samādhibalaṃ, "
"paññābalaṃ."
msgstr ""
"The powers of faith, energy, conscience, prudence, mindfulness, immersion, "
"and wisdom."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an7.4:2.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, saddhābalaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the power of faith?"

msgctxt "an7.4:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako saddho hoti, saddahati tathāgatassa bodhiṃ:"
msgstr "It’s when a noble disciple has faith in the Realized One’s awakening:"

msgctxt "an7.4:2.3"
msgid ""
"‘itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho "
"bhagavā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘That Blessed One is perfected, a fully awakened Buddha, accomplished in "
"knowledge and conduct, holy, knower of the world, supreme guide for those "
"who wish to train, teacher of gods and humans, awakened, blessed.’"

msgctxt "an7.4:2.4"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, saddhābalaṃ. (1)"
msgstr "This is called the power of faith."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an7.4:3.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, vīriyabalaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the power of energy?"

msgctxt "an7.4:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako āraddhavīriyo viharati akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"pahānāya, kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ upasampadāya, thāmavā daḷhaparakkamo "
"anikkhittadhuro kusalesu dhammesu."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant lives with energy roused up for giving up unskillful "
"qualities and gaining skillful qualities. They’re strong, staunchly "
"vigorous, not slacking off when it comes to developing skillful qualities."

msgctxt "an7.4:3.3"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, vīriyabalaṃ. (2)"
msgstr "This is called the power of energy."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.4"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an7.4:4.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, hirībalaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the power of conscience?"

msgctxt "an7.4:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako hirīmā hoti, hirīyati kāyaduccaritena "
"vacīduccaritena manoduccaritena, hirīyati pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"samāpattiyā."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a noble disciple has a conscience. They’re conscientious about bad "
"conduct by way of body, speech, and mind, and conscientious about acquiring "
"any bad, unskillful qualities."

msgctxt "an7.4:4.3"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, hirībalaṃ. (3)"
msgstr "This is called the power of conscience."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an7.4:5.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, ottappabalaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the power of prudence?"

msgctxt "an7.4:5.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako ottappī hoti, ottappati kāyaduccaritena "
"vacīduccaritena manoduccaritena, ottappati pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"samāpattiyā."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a noble disciple is prudent. They’re prudent when it comes to bad "
"conduct by way of body, speech, and mind, and prudent when it comes to the "
"acquiring of any bad, unskillful qualities."

msgctxt "an7.4:5.3"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, ottappabalaṃ. (4)"
msgstr "This is called the power of prudence."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an7.4:6.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, satibalaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the power of mindfulness?"

msgctxt "an7.4:6.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako satimā hoti paramena satinepakkena samannāgato "
"cirakatampi cirabhāsitampi saritā anussaritā."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a noble disciple is mindful. They have utmost mindfulness and "
"alertness, and can remember and recall what was said and done long ago."

msgctxt "an7.4:6.3"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, satibalaṃ. (5)"
msgstr "This is called the power of mindfulness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an7.4:7.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, samādhibalaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the power of immersion?"

msgctxt "an7.4:7.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako vivicceva kāmehi … pe …"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant, quite secluded from sensual pleasures, secluded from "
"unskillful qualities, enters and remains in the first absorption, which has "
"the rapture and bliss born of seclusion, while placing the mind and keeping "
"it connected. …"

msgctxt "an7.4:7.3"
msgid ""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.4:7.4"
msgid "catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"Giving up pleasure and pain, and ending former happiness and sadness, they "
"enter and remain in the fourth absorption, without pleasure or pain, with "
"pure equanimity and mindfulness."

msgctxt "an7.4:7.5"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, samādhibalaṃ. (6)"
msgstr "This is called the power of immersion."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an7.4:8.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, paññābalaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the power of wisdom?"

msgctxt "an7.4:8.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako paññavā hoti udayatthagāminiyā paññāya "
"samannāgato ariyāya nibbedhikāya sammā dukkhakkhayagāminiyā."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a noble disciple is wise. They have the wisdom of arising and "
"passing away which is noble, penetrative, and leads to the complete ending "
"of suffering."

msgctxt "an7.4:8.3"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, paññābalaṃ. (7)"
msgstr "This is called the power of wisdom."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an7.4:9.1"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, satta balānīti."
msgstr "These are the seven powers.”"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an7.4:10.1"
msgid "Saddhābalaṃ vīriyañca,"
msgstr "“The powers are faith and energy,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.4:10.2"
msgid "hirī ottappiyaṃ balaṃ;"
msgstr "conscience and prudence,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.4:10.3"
msgid "Satibalaṃ samādhi ca,"
msgstr "mindfulness and immersion,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.4:10.4"
msgid "paññā ve sattamaṃ balaṃ;"
msgstr "and wisdom as the seventh power."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.4:10.5"
msgid "Etehi balavā bhikkhu,"
msgstr "Empowered by these,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.4:10.6"
msgid "sukhaṃ jīvati paṇḍito."
msgstr "an astute mendicant lives happily."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an7.4:11.1"
msgid "Yoniso vicine dhammaṃ,"
msgstr "They should examine the teaching rationally,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.4:11.2"
msgid "paññāyatthaṃ vipassati;"
msgstr "discerning the meaning with wisdom."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.4:11.3"
msgid "Pajjotasseva nibbānaṃ,"
msgstr "The liberation of their heart"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.4:11.4"
msgid "vimokkho hoti cetaso”ti."
msgstr "is like a lamp going out.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.4:11.5"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
